11. Make a comparison between:-

1. Generalization and abstraction
2. Learning that is guided and unsupervised
3. Regression and classification

Ans.	i.generalization is something which can be used in any case while abstraction is case-specific and cannot be used always 

Ii.	guided learning is like learning from teachers or supervised learning as in this whenever we make a mistake we know how can we get to the correct answer wherelese in unsupervised learning we don't have the answers with us we try to cluster all the similar data together in clusters 
Iii.	


classification is when we want to classify/distinguish between two or more classes like when we want to classify apples from oranges. Regression is when we want to predict a value from a continuous number line like the salary of an employee.




















